var let const 

1. Var - use from beginning of js
It is global scope
It is local inside function (funtrion scope)
Inside blocks like for-while-if-else it is still global 
and can change value of global inside it 
It is hosted means can be use before declwar
It can be redeclear

2. Let and const 
Added after 2016
Let and const are block scoped means exist inside block 
outside block it dont exist 
Hosted on top but cant use before declear
both cant be redeclewared and const cant be rewrite
